setwd("C:/Users/USER/Documents/warsztaty_badawcze/sem_letni")

dane<-readRDS("table_rms.rds", refhook = NULL)
dane$result<-ifelse(dane$result=="No credit",1,ifelse(
  dane$result=="Partial credit",2,3)
)
dane$timing<-dane$timing/60000
dane1 <- dane %>% group_by(position,CNT,clus_short) %>% 
  filter(!is.na(W_FSTUWT) & !is.na(timing) & 
           !is.na(n.actions) & !is.na(result_num) ) %>% 
  summarise(
    timing=round(weighted.mean(timing,W_FSTUWT,na.rm=TRUE),2),
    result=round(weighted.mean(result,W_FSTUWT,na.rm=TRUE),2)
  )
dane_small<-dane1
dane_small<-dane_small%>% group_by(position)

dane_small_1<-dane_small %>% select(position,result,CNT)
daneMin <- dane_small_1 %>% 
  group_by(position,CNT) %>% 
  filter(result == min(result, na.rm=TRUE) )

daneMax <- dane_small_1 %>% 
  group_by(position,CNT) %>% 
  filter(result == max(result, na.rm=TRUE) )
theme_ggplain <- theme_bw() + theme(panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color="white"), axis.ticks=element_line(size=0), axis.text=element_text(size=0))
dane_small$position <- reorder(dane_small$position, dane_small$result, median, na.rm=TRUE)

NajniÅ¼szy score w kaÅ¼dej pozycji dla kaÅ¼dego kraju, punktami pokazany jest Å›redni czas

ggplot(dane_small, aes(x=position, y=result,label=CNT)) +
  geom_violin(scale="width", aes(fill=position), color="white", alpha=0.4) + 
  geom_jitter(aes(size=timing),position=position_jitter(width = .45, height = 0),
              shape=16) +
  geom_rug(sides = "l") + 
  geom_text(data=daneMin, vjust=2, color="blue3") + 
  theme_bw() + xlab("position") + theme( panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color="white"))

NajwyÅ¼szy score w kaÅ¼dej pozycji dla kaÅ¼dego kraju, punktami pokazany jest Å›redni czas

ggplot(dane_small, aes(x=position, y=result,label=CNT)) +
  geom_violin(scale="width", aes(fill=position), color="white", alpha=0.4) + 
  geom_jitter(aes(size=timing),position=position_jitter(width = .45, height = 0),
              shape=16) +
  geom_rug(sides = "l") + 
  geom_text(data=daneMax, vjust=-1, color="blue3") + 
  theme_bw() + xlab("position") + theme( panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color="white"))

LICZBA AKCJI I SCORE

dane2 <- dane %>% group_by(position,CNT,clus_short) %>% 
  filter(!is.na(W_FSTUWT) & !is.na(timing) & 
           !is.na(n.actions) & !is.na(result_num) ) %>% 
  summarise(
    n.actions=round(weighted.mean(n.actions,W_FSTUWT,na.rm=TRUE),2),
    result=round(weighted.mean(result,W_FSTUWT,na.rm=TRUE),2)
  )
dane_small<-dane2
dane_small<-dane_small%>% group_by(position)

dane_small_1<-dane_small %>% select(position,n.actions,CNT)
daneMin <- dane_small_1 %>% 
  group_by(position,CNT) %>% 
  filter(n.actions == min(n.actions, na.rm=TRUE) )

daneMax <- dane_small_1 %>% 
  group_by(position,CNT) %>% 
  filter(n.actions == max(n.actions, na.rm=TRUE) )
theme_ggplain <- theme_bw() + theme(panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color="white"), axis.ticks=element_line(size=0), axis.text=element_text(size=0))
dane_small$position <- reorder(dane_small$position, dane_small$n.actions, median, na.rm=TRUE)

Najmniejsza liczba akcji w kaÅ¼dej pozycji dla kaÅ¼dego kraju, punktami pokazany jest Å›redni wynik

ggplot(dane_small, aes(x=position, y=n.actions,label=CNT)) +

              shape=16) +
  geom_rug(sides = "l") + 
  geom_text(data=daneMin, vjust=2, color="blue3") + 
  theme_bw() + xlab("position") + theme( panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color="white"))
